title: 1 Bed, Fireplaces available, Oversized closets
posting_body: ["Embrace classic comfort and contemporary style at 3300 Tamarac Apartments, in Denver's Hampden neighborhood.", 'Our collection of refined studio, 1 & 2 bedroom apartments offer you a place to rest, relax, and have a little fun.', 'From our relaxed modern style and upscale social spaces to chic interiors, youll be ready to unwind in no time.', '-Worry-free 24-hour onsite maintenance', '-Virtual Moving Concierge: Complimentary address change, set up home services and digital moving announcements', '-Oversized closets', '-Pet friendly (breed restrictions apply)', '-Fitness center with free weights and cardio machines                                                                                         Featured amenity', '-Elevator access', '-Landscaped courtyards and ponds with outdoor seating', '-Ceiling fans in living areas and bedrooms', '-Wood-style plank flooring in kitchen and living areas', '-Easy access to public transportation', '-Separate dining area', '-Fenced dog park with pet watering station', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', 'Equal Housing Opportunity', 'Prices Change Daily', 'Flexible Lease Terms']
